attributes.description:
1 Owner
Spare key
FSH with Toyota
Finance can be arranged
Trade in welcome
Delivery country wide
Toyota introduced a new, Thailand-built Yaris to the market featuring assertive exterior and interior styling. A naturally-aspirated 1.5-litre petrol engine does service under the bonnet with 79 kW and 140 Nm of torque and is offered with a 5-speed manual gearbox. As a result of these changes, mostly its newly chiselled and mature aesthetics, I expect the new Yaris is going to find itself on the shopping radar of more men than any of its predecessors. Yes, it still retains that excellent reliability and fuel economy as before, but the total package and gearing towards a return to the driver’s car means that the new Yaris has far more Y chromosome in its makeup than ever before. And that’s nothing to be ashamed of.
